cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper deals with machine learning algorithms applied to dynamic and noisy environments. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also deals with robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY) in the context of the mountain car problem.
